<plot>REWRITTEN ARIAS. Maria arrives at a mansion she has inherited. The mansion is ruled by the devilish Bruno who wants to scare Maria away forever. Maria befriends Laszlo, a night porter at the village hotel, who has to protect her against the evil Bruno. The operatic plot serves as a vehicle to performances of eight famous opera arias with new lyrics.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?161704</url></doc>
